  },
  "summary": {
    "zh": "史蒂夫·伦德尔著，机械工业出版社出版的 F1 赛车工程技术图解，涵盖 1950 年至今的技术演进与当代赛车各系统原理，含大量 Giorgio Piola 技术图与 Motorsport Images 历史影像。",
    "en": "Steve Rendle's illustrated reference on F1 car engineering and the evolution of technology from 1950 to the present, with Giorgio Piola technical drawings and Motorsport Images photography."
  },
